<para style="p">

  <verse number="1" style="v" />Finally, my brothers, rejoice in the Lord. For me to write these same things again to you is not bothersome. These things will keep you safe.

  <verse number="2" style="v" />Watch out for the dogs. Watch out for the evil workers. Watch out for the mutilation.

  <verse number="3" style="v" />For we are the circumcision. It is we who worship by the Spirit of God. It is we who take pride in Christ Jesus, and who have no confidence in the flesh.
